      <title>地图可视化工具folium教程</title>
      <link>https://rosefinch-midsummer.github.io/zh/posts/tech/%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%86%E5%8C%96%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7folium%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</link>
